# Intro

we are using unsloth for 4bit quantization for our model
our model is "Qwen3-1.7B-unsloth-bnb-4bit"

## Task
Finetune the model to make it better at translating kapampangan into english

## Dataset
this if from huggingface [Kapampangan - English Sentences](https://huggingface.co/datasets/Coco-18/Kapampangan-English/viewer/default/train?p=4)

## Steps
1. Install required dependencies
2. Load the model 
3. Test the model without being fine tuned
4. Initiate QLoRa for fine tuning
5. Set up the Dataset
6. Fine Tune the Model
7. Inference the fine tuned model
8. Benchmark BLEU and CHRF raw model and fine tuned model
9. Save to Drive

## Output

|**Metric**|**Raw Model (Base)**|**Fine-Tuned Model**|**Improvement**|
|---|---|---|---|
|**BLEU Score**|0.03|**72.01**|**+71.98**|
|**chrF Score**|4.61|**69.78**|**+65.17**|
